17:36.131 --> 17:38.675
- Oh, ho, ho!
- (LAUGHTER)

17:38.699 --> 17:40.977
Yup, it is Mommy's turn.

17:41.001 --> 17:43.881
(LAUGHS)

17:43.905 --> 17:48.373
Um, how would we make up
for... your lost income?

17:49.376 --> 17:50.576
Four to five mill.

17:52.212 --> 17:53.612
It's just an option.

17:54.614 --> 17:55.958
That's a great option for you.

17:55.982 --> 18:00.296
Yeah, yeah, 'cause taking care
of her all day is really easy.

18:00.320 --> 18:02.119
- No work at all.
- (SIGHS)

18:04.257 --> 18:06.436
Look... Ash...

18:06.460 --> 18:08.671
