happy doing what they do,

18:16.101 --> 18:19.380
so if this opportunity
isn't gonna make you happy,

18:19.404 --> 18:22.183
do not do it. We'll be fine.

18:22.207 --> 18:24.319
♪ ♪

18:24.343 --> 18:25.754
(SIGHS)

18:25.778 --> 18:27.889
- Oh my gosh.
- (SQUEALS)

18:27.913 --> 18:29.078
- (CLICKING)
- (CHUCKLES)

18:30.348 --> 18:32.359
(SQUEALS)
