18:32.383 --> 18:34.094
(LAUGHTER)

18:34.118 --> 18:36.129
MALCOLM: That is the best yet.

18:36.153 --> 18:38.131
- Yes.
- (LAUGHS)

18:38.155 --> 18:41.335
ASHLEY: I just... I'm just
thinking about the future,

18:41.359 --> 18:45.272
the possibility of long-lasting
generational wealth

18:45.296 --> 18:47.607
for Hailey's safety,

18:47.631 --> 18:49.041
for ours.

18:49.065 --> 18:51.578
