about it all you want,

18:51.602 --> 18:53.847
but the future's gonna be
what the future's gonna be.

18:53.871 --> 18:55.704
See? And that's what scares me.

18:57.007 --> 18:59.953
We just left her there. She was not well.

18:59.977 --> 19:03.388
