committed, if that's what you think?

19:36.244 --> 19:37.876
NAVID: What's going on?

19:45.285 --> 19:46.552
- Is he...
- No.

19:47.354 --> 19:48.899
- NAVID: Should I stay?
- LAYLA: No.

19:48.923 --> 19:50.901
Go. Have fun. Okay?

19:50.925 --> 19:52.713
Just keep your phone charged.

19:54.694 --> 19:56.561
Are you seeing that girl?

19:58.364 --> 19:59.697
Kristen.

20:00.767 --> 20:03.412
But why, Navid-jan. Why?

20:03.436 --> 20:05.681
