20:05.705 --> 20:07.038
You're all banged up.

20:09.609 --> 20:11.074
Really?

20:12.310 --> 20:15.946
♪ ♪

20:23.088 --> 20:24.588
(SIGHS)

20:36.634 --> 20:37.900
