20:39.336 --> 20:41.011
We're afraid of you, Farid.

20:41.606 --> 20:43.772
We're afraid of what's happening to you.

20:46.476 --> 20:48.876
What's happening to me
is happening for a reason.

20:52.782 --> 20:54.649
What if that reason is...

20:55.819 --> 20:57.619
simply punishment?

21:00.189 --> 21:03.256
♪ ♪

21:27.115 --> 21:28.180
CARMEN: Mm.

21:29.316 --> 21:30.616
- Here.
- (SIGHS)

21:31.686 --> 21:32.938
Right?

21:37.824 --> 21:38.857
Whoa.

21:39.860 --> 21:42.426
That's a lot of pain.

21:44.116 --> 21:45.530
Old pain.

21:49.502 --> 21:51.369
You poor boy.

21:55.775 --> 21:56.985
Duc.

21:57.009 --> 21:59.054
I am so sorry

21:59.078 --> 22:01.156
you had to suffer like this...

22:01.180 --> 22:03.513
- (DUC CRYING)
- ...for so long.

22:05.985 --> 22:07.651
You can let this go.

22:08.788 --> 22:10.665
