22:40.918 --> 22:43.851
What is it? It's... it's not working.

22:46.856 --> 22:48.555
So, what's going on?

22:49.792 --> 22:52.392
- Are you not into me?
- Of course I'm into you.

22:53.262 --> 22:55.362
- I just...
- You just what?

22:57.734 --> 23:01.201
We did it, like, once,
and now it's expected.

23:03.671 --> 23:05.739
You brought a condom.

23:09.211 --> 23:11.244
I'm sorry. It's just...

23:12.147 --> 23:14.881
- too fast or being in this car...
- Or what?

23:16.084 --> 23:17.828
Just say it.

23:17.852 --> 23:21.553
I just don't... think this is who I am.

23:22.556 --> 23:26.625
What? A guy who... has sex?

23:27.694 --> 23:29.305
A guy who has sex with girls?

23:29.329 --> 23:33.043
- No, that's not even...
- Or a guy who has sex with me?

23:33.067 --> 23:36.746
♪ With you riding shotgun,
speeding 'cause... ♪

23:36.770 --> 23:38.564
It's just...

23:38.805 --> 23:41.483
it feels like everything's
changed all of a sudden, and...

23:41.507 --> 23:44.686
Oh, what? What? You feel smothered?

23:44.710 --> 23:47.256
(SCOFFS) You need your space?

23:47.280 --> 23:51.060
Wow. What a fucking cliché.

23:51.084 --> 23:53.027
