23:53.051 --> 23:54.863
You need to get your shit together, dude.

23:54.887 --> 23:56.987
- (GEARSHIFT CLICKS)
- Kristen.

24:00.392 --> 24:03.493
(CRICKETS CHIRPING)

24:28.618 --> 24:31.686
♪ ♪

25:07.155 --> 25:09.856
DUC: <i>I've always felt like
I should've saved her...</i>

25:10.758 --> 25:12.424
from those men.

25:13.627 --> 25:15.105
Of course.

25:15.129 --> 25:17.162
You were five years old.

25:18.332 --> 25:20.877
Children make themselves responsible.

25:20.901 --> 25:23.146
It's easier than accepting chaos.

25:23.170 --> 25:25.681
It's all just chaos, isn't it?

25:26.272 --> 25:28.105
CARMEN: Well, not just.

25:30.810 --> 25:33.345
What's the worst thing
that's ever happened to you?

25:34.580 --> 25:36.713
(CHUCKLES)

25:38.650 --> 25:40.417
What a lovely question.

25:43.990 --> 25:46.801
My father died in a car accident.

25:46.825 --> 25:49.137
