25:49.161 --> 25:50.794
I was 11 years old.

25:51.997 --> 25:53.507
Oh my God.

25:53.531 --> 25:55.943
It wasn't an ongoing trauma like yours,

25:55.967 --> 25:59.302
but it was one big surprise trauma.

26:01.006 --> 26:02.906
- I'm so sorry.
- Mmm.

26:06.244 --> 26:07.643
