26:12.116 --> 26:16.096
I just realized I haven't had
explosive diarrhea in a while.

26:16.120 --> 26:18.265
(LAUGHS)

26:18.289 --> 26:20.655
The bathroom's right through there.

26:33.069 --> 26:34.402
Thank you.

26:35.972 --> 26:37.671
Thank you.

26:51.353 --> 26:52.953
I'm turning in.

26:55.690 --> 26:56.990
Night.

26:59.683 --> 27:01.683
_

