39:38.841 --> 39:40.552
- I'm here.
- I know.

39:40.576 --> 39:42.843
(SNIFFLES) I know. Thank you.

39:47.582 --> 39:49.916
- (LOCK CLICKS)
- I need to tell somebody...

39:52.187 --> 39:53.698
and I can't tell Audrey, because I know

39:53.722 --> 39:55.432
that she's been very unhappy.

39:55.456 --> 39:57.166
I always know that.

39:57.759 --> 40:00.104
But, uh, I never call her.

40:00.128 --> 40:02.505
She's got so much to take
care of, so many people.

40:02.529 --> 40:05.809
Well, she wouldn't mind,
if you called, Ike, I'm sure.

40:05.833 --> 40:07.878
No, that's... this isn't what
I wanted to talk about.

40:07.902 --> 40:09.068
Okay.

40:14.541 --> 40:15.874
You changed your book.

40:16.944 --> 40:20.122
(HESITANTLY) Um, I don't think I did.

40:20.146 --> 40:23.047
