40:38.230 --> 40:40.563
She hasn't told me anything about Ramon.

40:42.400 --> 40:43.945
What about... What about him?

40:43.969 --> 40:45.769
You know why I trust you?

40:48.140 --> 40:50.040
Do you remember when I first met Ramon?

40:51.143 --> 40:52.886
He was a little baby,
and he was sleeping,

40:52.910 --> 40:54.188
you let me hold him,

40:54.212 --> 40:56.957
- and I dropped him?
- Yeah, I remember.

40:56.981 --> 40:59.893
