Well, he's on fire again.

40:59.917 --> 41:01.962
♪ ♪

41:01.986 --> 41:04.086
Wh-what exactly...

41:05.589 --> 41:07.434
do you mean?

41:08.231 --> 41:09.864
Okay.

41:11.161 --> 41:14.229
Um, I'm on a different medication...

41:16.399 --> 41:18.133
Plus I got old...

41:20.103 --> 41:22.237
so when I see things...

41:25.142 --> 41:27.465
When I see things,
I know they're not there,

41:28.177 --> 41:30.744
