make me feel crazy like Audrey did.

41:44.425 --> 41:47.493
How is Ramon on fire again?

41:51.732 --> 41:54.133
Do things feel normal to you?

41:55.536 --> 41:58.015
Oh, what... what is normal?

41:58.039 --> 42:00.539
Don't you feel like something's wrong?

42:02.976 --> 42:05.376
I do. I... I do.

42:06.246 --> 42:07.490
See, I've always felt...

42:07.514 --> 42:09.292
well, I mean, since I've gotten sick

42:09.316 --> 42:11.983
I've always felt that way,
but it's gotten worse.

42:14.054 --> 42:16.487
It's outside of me.

42:18.925 --> 42:19.990
Yeah.

42:20.893 --> 42:22.793
It's everywhere.

42:29.936 --> 42:34.371
♪ ♪

42:42.881 --> 42:45.748
