42:57.394 --> 42:59.472
Okay. We could go out somewhere.

42:59.496 --> 43:02.731
It's a beautiful day. Yeah, let's go out.

43:04.501 --> 43:07.002
Or... not.

43:27.356 --> 43:28.421
Okay.

