44:20.439 --> 44:22.384
Oh, yeah, absolutely.

44:22.408 --> 44:24.185
- Great.
- Sure.

44:24.209 --> 44:26.221
We look forward to your counter.

44:26.245 --> 44:28.478
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

44:30.482 --> 44:32.115
Um, Ashley.

44:33.118 --> 44:36.196
You're not thinking
of bagging on this, are you?

44:36.220 --> 44:39.533
