make me look really bad.

44:39.557 --> 44:41.953
- Okay.
- I was just joking about

44:41.978 --> 44:44.504
the double-boxer stuff before.

44:44.528 --> 44:46.573
- I swear.
- I just need to make one call.

44:46.597 --> 44:47.896
- Okay.
- (BOTH CHUCKLE)

44:51.734 --> 44:53.846
MALCOLM: <i>Just focus on what you want.</i>

44:53.870 --> 44:55.971
Okay? Life is too short not to.

44:56.806 --> 44:58.117
Okay. I'm not gonna take it.

44:58.141 --> 45:00.886
- I'm not gonna take it.
- MALCOLM: <i> Wow.</i>

45:00.910 --> 45:03.423
What "wow"? "Wow" like, that's a
gutsy move and you're proud of me,

45:03.447 --> 45:05.058
or "wow" as in you're disappointed?

45:05.082 --> 45:08.327
MALCOLM: <i>No, not disappointed. Surprised.</i>

45:08.351 --> 45:10.262
I guess you really convinced me

45:10.286 --> 45:12.831
that all that money would make us safer.

45:12.855 --> 45:13.999
You know, I mean,

45:14.023 --> 45:16.823
who knows what's gonna happen
in this fucking country?

45:18.394 --> 45:19.671
So, you think I should take it?

45:19.695 --> 45:21.706
MALCOLM: <i>I didn't say that. I...</i>

45:22.033 --> 45:23.708
<i>What... what I'm saying is...</i>

45:24.398 --> 45:25.531
<i>look...</i>

45:27.535 --> 45:31.070
