45:32.607 --> 45:35.819
- (BIRDS CAWING)
- (WINGS FLUTTERING)

45:35.843 --> 45:39.245
♪ ♪

45:45.619 --> 45:46.863
(KNOCKS ON DOOR)

45:46.887 --> 45:49.587
♪ ♪

46:00.566 --> 46:03.267
(DOORBELL CHIMES)

46:12.878 --> 46:14.111
What are you doing here?

46:15.581 --> 46:17.858
I'm here to say goodbye.

46:17.882 --> 46:20.928
My mom's waiting out front.
She's leaving my dad.

46:20.952 --> 46:22.252
Oh my God.

46:24.656 --> 46:25.633
Why?

46:25.657 --> 46:26.756
It's, um...

46:27.759 --> 46:28.824
He's...

46:29.727 --> 46:31.261
It doesn't matter.

46:32.764 --> 46:34.207
I have to go with her.

46:34.231 --> 46:37.911
- Where?
