46:37.935 --> 46:39.935
Oh God. You're going to San Francisco?

46:41.205 --> 46:44.117
That's insane. You could just stay here.

46:44.141 --> 46:46.345
- Kristen.
- Wait. No, I know my parents

46:46.370 --> 46:47.620
are not gonna care.

46:47.644 --> 46:49.956
Then you won't have
to, like, miss school.

46:49.980 --> 46:51.623
School is over in two weeks anyways.

46:51.647 --> 46:53.781
Well, how long are you gone for?

46:55.518 --> 46:56.684
I don't know.

47:01.458 --> 47:02.435
No.

47:02.459 --> 47:03.902
(SNIFFLES)

47:03.926 --> 47:05.593
No, I don't want you to go.

47:06.762 --> 47:08.055
I mean...

47:08.897 --> 47:11.909
I know that things are weird with
us, but you're my only friend.

47:11.933 --> 47:15.001
I know. I'll miss you too, but...

47:16.472 --> 47:18.338
I have to go with my mom.

47:19.774 --> 47:20.840
So...

47:22.478 --> 47:23.810
bye.

47:32.086 --> 47:33.219
(CRYING)

47:36.790 --> 47:39.169
We'll stay in touch. Promise.

47:39.193 --> 47:40.904
Do you hate me?

47:40.928 --> 47:42.438
Of course not.

47:42.462 --> 47:45.163
I was... I was kind of a bitch to you.

47:47.100 --> 47:49.900
- Yeah. You were.
- (BOTH CHUCKLE)

48:05.584 --> 48:06.650
Bye.

48:20.632 --> 48:22.198
(GASPS)

48:27.938 --> 48:29.705
I'm so ashamed. I...

48:31.709 --> 48:33.341
I just couldn't stop.

48:34.311 --> 48:35.377
(SIGHS)

48:36.480 --> 48:38.062
I'm too weak.

48:38.715 --> 48:40.627
Maybe this was something you needed to do

48:40.651 --> 48:42.750
for reasons you don't understand yet.

48:47.658 --> 48:49.468
I envy you. I...

48:49.492 --> 48:51.770
I see your faith. I see it's goodness.

48:51.794 --> 48:53.460
I really do.

48:55.598 --> 48:57.176
I feel its comfort.

48:57.200 --> 48:58.566
(GASPS)

49:03.739 --> 49:06.184
Why did I meet Ramon?

49:06.208 --> 49:09.141
Why did he dream
of my mother mutilating herself?

49:10.278 --> 49:12.078
His seeing my past...

49:15.850 --> 49:18.218
What does it all mean? I'm...

49:19.254 --> 49:21.321
Wh-wh... what am I supposed to do?

49:22.990 --> 49:25.935
You know, in Islam,
the need to have all the answers

49:25.959 --> 49:28.493
is considered a kind of heresy.

49:32.165 --> 49:33.951
I'm a big sinner then.

49:34.568 --> 49:35.945
I've spent my life,

49:35.969 --> 49:38.303
I make my living searching for answers.

49:40.640 --> 49:42.172
Should I stop?

49:43.643 --> 49:46.344
"Islam" literally means "surrender."

