to be something watching...

50:32.629 --> 50:34.061
for anything to exist.

50:35.158 --> 50:36.636
(SIGHS)

50:36.660 --> 50:38.326
And that something is...

50:40.863 --> 50:42.397
God?

50:44.701 --> 50:47.067
Do you know what I take as proof of God?

50:49.204 --> 50:51.037
This moment right here.

50:53.975 --> 50:57.143
I have a chance to be of service
to a fellow man in need...

50:58.213 --> 51:00.246
