51:26.406 --> 51:28.239
<i>whether we'd like it to or not...</i>

51:29.976 --> 51:32.711
<i>no matter how much optimism we have...</i>

51:33.580 --> 51:36.013
<i>or how much we believe in...</i>

51:37.851 --> 51:41.084
<i>rational thought or God or...</i>

51:42.822 --> 51:43.998
aliens.

51:44.022 --> 51:46.089
There's no such thing as aliens.

51:46.959 --> 51:48.559
- You don't think?
- No.

51:49.395 --> 51:50.339
No, 'cause if there were,

51:50.363 --> 51:52.140
