52:17.488 --> 52:18.598
Why not?

52:18.622 --> 52:21.490
Because I... I was never on fire.

52:23.394 --> 52:24.404
(CLICKS)

52:25.041 --> 52:27.074
You feel that?

52:29.466 --> 52:30.564
Feel what?

52:31.601 --> 52:33.100
It's here.

52:38.474 --> 52:39.951
